{"tid":1890991,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我地搞咗個 Youtube channel 講國際關係 想大家幫幫手","createTime":"2020-02-21T13:21:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T14:13:32.000Z","uid":313480,"like":36,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"cc6f1c289cd84daa481274d8459e62163f151cd8","tid":1890991,"uid":313480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T13:21:19.000Z","msg":"我地 The Glocal 全球政經評論 啱啱開始搞 Youtube channel <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好希望透過唔同媒體同大家擴闊國際視野，以及多啲用呢個角度去分析唔同時事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n我地個 channel 依家都仲係處於摸索階段，嚟緊亦會由淺入深咁出啲 conceptual 嘅野。希望大家幫幫手畀吓意見同埋講低對咩 Topic 有興趣。唔該哂大家！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U_DwQwf2gAk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DU_DwQwf2gAk&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVOzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=7e716400\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U_DwQwf2gAk</a>"},{"pid":"0721eefe06e98f7d2d167f42c4b455b0f31901c9","tid":1890991,"uid":99420,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T13:27:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"767eb388ae2fdb62a72ad165ea72b020d7bed491","tid":1890991,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T13:28:19.000Z","msg":"Sorry 阻住你睇文<br />\nP牌樓主唔想再有手足被黑警自殺<br />\n<br />\n呢<del>4</del><strong>8</strong>個apps 啱所有人用，尤其前線手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1864933/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1864933/</a><br />\n<br />\n啲apps可以避免黑警link 到你同你嘅online identity、阻嚇黑警上門&ldquo;被自殺&rdquo;手足、俾你㩒個制就通知信得過嘅人你遇咩危險，trigger alarm 並附上GPS、自動增加你拍嘅相/片嘅可信性<br />\n<br />\n請大家幫推，避免沉底"},{"pid":"204571b554390cd18cc47648a6b69cc0c2e56288","tid":1890991,"uid":94475,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T13:41:23.000Z","msg":"沈旭暉係咪你哋老細？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\